headline: Eagle Materials (EXP) Lags Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: Eagle Materials (EXP) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.76% and +0.96%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
